snippet.title: This Is the President - How To Get Rid Of A Supreme Court Judge
snippet.description:
Have you ever found yourself wondering "How can I get rid of two Supreme Court Judges in under 8 minutes?" Well, this video might provide you with some ideas on how to achieve that - in This Is the President.

If only the good men and women of the Supreme Court weren't so stubborn, they could keep their positions.. and their lives. But if they are standing in the way of getting the 28th Amendment to the Consitution passed, well, accidents happen, right? And if they don't happen naturally, then maybe the situation requires a little help from your friends.
